Title: Night Market concerts
Content: OrientXpress will be playing two concerts in July as part of a Shanghai night of love weekend at the Night Market, Cuba St, Wellington. 8pm-9pm, July 1 and July 2

Title: Old St Paul's concert
Content: OrientXpress will be playing a concert at Old St Paul's, Mulgrave St. Noon-1pm, July 12. See you there!!
